Okay so I cried during the entire video, you guys looked amazing and your venue was so amazing! I got married a year ago, and all of the emotions just came back, the dress shopping, the venue planning and walking down the isle, seeing my husband to be for the first time. We even finished part of the dress in the morning, and we got married at 11 am 😂😂😂
A small part of me regret not saving up and spending more time planning the wedding (planned in like, 4 months max) but we still got things the way we wanted, and well, got married ❤❤❤
